 baking paper, secure with string or an elastic band and put into Varoma dish."},{"content":"Place water in mixing bowl and place covered Varoma into position. Steam puddings <b>60 min\/Varoma\/speed 2<b> or until a skewer inserted in centre comes out clean."},{"content":"Remove from basins and invert onto serving plates. Serve hot with custard, cream or ice cream."}],"basicInfo":["easy","10m","1h 10m","4 portions"]}